text: IN PICTURES: 300,000 doses of #China's Sinopharm #vaccine arrived in #Ethiopia yesterday. The country is facing an ongoing spike in new #COVID19 cases. These jabs represent the first shipment of #coronavirus vaccines that Ethiopia has received outside of the #COVAX scheme. 🇪🇹🤝🇨🇳 https://t.co/YkjJNxsZmR
